Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.02,0:22:14.81,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HFF00FF&}{\bord2}{\pos(522,306)}{\fs25}{\fad(0,300)}真唯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.38,0:22:16.54,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我要教你们2个要点
